{"tid":2410484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日梁凌杰逝世20個月　太古廣場附近　有市民到場獻花悼念","createTime":"2021-02-16T15:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T16:08:34.000Z","uid":261647,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf96cf212881ef16cf81b6170b766811d238db9d","tid":2410484,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photographicsocietyhk/posts/518340149565035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphotographicsocietyhk%2Fposts%2F518340149565035&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=3615b03a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photographicsocietyhk/posts/518340149565035</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：PSHK<br />\n<br />\n【15/2 梁凌杰逝世 20 個月 金鐘有悼念活動 王婆婆籲拒「安心出行」】<br />\n<br />\n今日（15日）是梁凌杰墮樓逝世 20 個月，在他墮下的太古廣場附近，有市民到場獻上白花悼念。王婆婆在場依舊轉動她的黃色小傘，也在太古廣場對出花槽貼上「拒絕安心出行」應用程式等的海報。<br />\n<br />\n現場不時有數名軍裝警員在悼念花槽附近戒備，並於七時三十分左右用廣播呼籲市民切勿多於二人聚集。<br />\n<br />\n其間Tommy阮民安也有到場參與悼念活動，並與王婆婆相擁勉勵對方。<br />\n<br />\n攝:Sam , 何零解<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJ86D6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJ86D6g.jpg&h=b015068c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJF1sZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJF1sZE.jpg&h=a0607c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1h7ox2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1h7ox2.jpg&h=d3e82e00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d80ca11f3af5efa7a41fa0f52b9662e9381b2b1","tid":2410484,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry"},{"pid":"1e6bc68226508d7efb7645